  • java.lang.Object

    public class SanityCheckOfferServiceDecorator
extends java.lang.Object
implements DefaultOfferService
    Path Sanity check wrapper around DefaultOfferService. Ensures that all DefaultOfferService methods (current and future) properly implement file path sanity checks.
